{"tid":754864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］晚晚發惡夢是咪有問題","createTime":"2018-07-24T17:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T08:46:08.000Z","uid":147195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"440af3d5f955700a8c61560abef66f4afb530019","tid":754864,"uid":147195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 晚晚都會發惡夢然後紮醒<br />\n有時惡夢醒左就開始鬼壓床<br />\n一晚可以重覆三四次<br />\n<br />\n次次喊住醒 又喊到攰再瞓 再紮醒<br />\n會唔會係精神上有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾個月黎都係咁<br />\n本身情緒已經好唔穩定<br />\n又瞓唔到 有時合埋眼已經浮現左個畫面<br />\n<br />\n但只限係屋企瞓<br />\n去朋友度瞓甚至去camp都冇事<br />\n定係喺屋企有啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df98fd7c37c88ed5b28fbd0a34c0bc516dacae84","tid":754864,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"你屋企人會唔會好似你咁樣？"},{"pid":"742fc55c122c66231dfe83a316852a804c32f2dc","tid":754864,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"講下發咩惡夢<br />\n每次都同一個或者類似惡夢？"},{"pid":"8b96190c03e3768ab0db383bdf19f44dfbb564f4","tid":754864,"uid":133205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:04:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 去朋友度瞓甚至去camp都冇事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為你怕寂莫"},{"pid":"98479a6785821e796f030f353cf85e926a0e51a1","tid":754864,"uid":172677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:04:38.000Z","msg":"建議巴打睇吓衛斯理本尋夢先"},{"pid":"28d60f3a324bbab3086279392c865e13c012e55a","tid":754864,"uid":147195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df98fd7c37c88ed5b28fbd0a34c0bc516dacae84","tid":754864,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T